            <h2>What is Ramadan?</h2>
            <p>Ramadan is the ninth month of the Islamic lunar calendar, observed by Muslims worldwide as a month of fasting, prayer, reflection, and community. It is a time for spiritual growth, self-discipline, and empathy for those less fortunate.</p>
